        {
            "title": "日圓兌美元逼近160關口 日本財務大臣提到干預可能性",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GDYQ0jGlqpOjcqi0qpOnew--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2c121cd24a772ee3bfcdda552f902c66\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Bloomberg\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Bloomberg;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Bloomberg\">Bloomberg</a></figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 日本財務大臣表示，可能會採取「大膽行動」來應對匯率波動，指進行干預。當前日圓匯率接近日本當局2024年曾數次入市干預的關鍵水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「歸根結底要果斷應對，包括採取大膽措施，」日本財政大臣片山皋月周五就日圓疲軟回答問題時表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在她發表講話之前，日圓兌美元匯率在159.70附近波動，距離160關口僅一步之遙，而160正是當局上次出手干預支撐日圓匯率的水平。她發表講話後，日圓一度走強至159.46。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2e831e44-0ff6-341e-9f45-9fd06944cd3b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7tCv23ln5UOB60rODU3j1Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f826bc2a8f97ff6385b2c8f455a7e9dc\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美元勢創7月以來最佳單月表現 中東衝突攪亂華爾街匯率預期</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">片山皋月再次指出，投機性波動是由石油市場部分交易所驅動，表明她不僅關注貨幣市場，也在關注包括大宗商品等整體市場。知情人士稱，本周早些時候，日本財務省就可能干預原油期貨交易一事徵詢市場意見。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Japan’s Katayama Flags Possible Intervention as Yen Nears 160</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
